<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <script>
  // Verifica se o usuário já está logado
  if (localStorage.getItem("site_autenticado") !== "true") {
    // Se não estiver, redireciona imediatamente para a tela de login
    window.location.href = "login.html";
  }
</script>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@500;600&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<title>Hero Advocacia</title>

<style>

:root{

    --primary:#16263f;
    --secondary:#c8a86b;
    --text:#344054;
    --light:#f8f9fb;
    --white:#ffffff;

}

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{

font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
background:#fff;
color:var(--text);

}

.hero{

min-height:90vh;

display:flex;
align-items:center;

padding:80px 8%;

background:
linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.95),rgba(255,255,255,.95)),
url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1589829545856-d10d557cf95f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1800&q=80");

background-size:cover;
background-position:center;

}

.container{

max-width:1300px;
margin:auto;

display:grid;
grid-template-columns:1fr 500px;
gap:70px;
align-items:center;

}

.tag{

display:inline-block;

padding:8px 18px;

border:1px solid rgba(200,168,107,.4);

border-radius:50px;

color:var(--secondary);

font-size:.85rem;

letter-spacing:2px;

text-transform:uppercase;

margin-bottom:30px;

}

h1{

font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;

font-size:4rem;

line-height:1.05;

color:var(--primary);

margin-bottom:30px;

}

.hero p{

font-size:1.1rem;

line-height:1.8;

max-width:620px;

margin-bottom:40px;

}

.buttons{

display:flex;
gap:18px;
margin-bottom:45px;

}

.btn{

padding:17px 34px;

border-radius:8px;

font-weight:600;

text-decoration:none;

transition:.3s;

}

.primary{

background:var(--primary);

color:white;

}

.primary:hover{

background:#0d1a2e;

}

.outline{

border:1px solid var(--primary);

color:var(--primary);

}

.outline:hover{

background:var(--primary);

color:white;

}

.features{

display:flex;
gap:35px;
flex-wrap:wrap;

}

.feature{

display:flex;
align-items:center;
gap:10px;

font-size:.95rem;

}

.dot{

width:10px;
height:10px;

background:var(--secondary);

border-radius:50%;

}

.card{

background:white;

padding:40px;

border-radius:18px;

box-shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.08);

text-align:center;

}

.card img{

width:100%;

border-radius:14px;

margin-bottom:25px;

}

.card h3{

font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;

font-size:2rem;

color:var(--primary);

margin-bottom:8px;

}

.card span{

color:var(--secondary);

font-weight:600;

display:block;

margin-bottom:25px;

}

.stats{

display:grid;

grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);

gap:20px;

margin-top:30px;

}

.stats div{

padding:18px;

background:var(--light);

border-radius:10px;

}

.stats strong{

display:block;

font-size:1.6rem;

color:var(--primary);

margin-bottom:5px;

}

@media(max-width:960px){

.container{

grid-template-columns:1fr;

}

h1{

font-size:3rem;

}

.buttons{

flex-direction:column;

}

.features{

flex-direction:column;

gap:15px;

}

}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<section class="hero">

<div class="container">

<div>

<span class="tag">
Advocacia Trabalhista Empresarial
</span>

<h1>
Segurança jurídica para empresas que querem crescer com tranquilidade.
</h1>

<p>
Assessoria especializada para empresas que desejam prevenir passivos trabalhistas, reduzir riscos e tomar decisões estratégicas com respaldo jurídico.
</p>

<div class="buttons">

<a href="#" class="btn primary">
Agendar uma reunião
</a>

<a href="#" class="btn outline">
Conheça nossa atuação
</a>

</div>

<div class="features">

<div class="feature">
<div class="dot"></div>
Atendimento personalizado
</div>

<div class="feature">
<div class="dot"></div>
Consultoria preventiva
</div>

<div class="feature">
<div class="dot"></div>
Foco em empresas
</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="card">

<img src="/https://yata-apix-a428ff6d-c9e0-4943-a080-179963e1f03c.s3-object.locaweb.com.br/039494f9ceeb4a82a9c2a3a322d393b8.jpg">

<h3>
André Morais
</h3>

<span>
Advogado Trabalhista Empresarial
</span>

<p>
Atuação estratégica voltada à prevenção de conflitos, compliance trabalhista e assessoria jurídica para empresas de diversos segmentos.
</p>

<div class="stats">

<div>

<strong>+10</strong>

Anos

</div>

<div>

<strong>100%</strong>

Atendimento

</div>

<div>

<strong>Empresas</strong>

Consultoria

</div>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

</body>
</html>